&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key liaison between plant operations and cross-functional partners, including maintenance, engineering, and corporate CI teams to communicate process needs, issues, and improvement opportunities.&amp;nbsp; .&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support process trials, new product trials, and process or equipment changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position requires &amp;lt;10% travel&lt;/p&gt;
