&lt;p&gt;This role follows a &lt;strong&gt;1st shift&lt;/strong&gt; schedule, working from&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;6:15 AM to 2:45 PM&lt;/strong&gt;, with designated days off on&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Monday&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; and Tuesday.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
